room_title: Escape room "Locker Room" by Escape Room Palm Springs in Palm Springs
room_address: 2500 N. Palm Canyon Dr., #B3, Palm Springs, CA 92262
room_description: Trapped in an abandoned locker room, you and your team will battle wits with a sadistic serial killer.  Uncover the fate of the prisoners captured before you and if you’re clever enough, maybe you’ll save more than just yourselves. In this game, you’ll face both mental and physical challenges to test your mind and spirit.
